overview: Document storage can be a great way to organise your office. It clears up space, alleviates stress but most importantly saves you time and money by eliminating the need for your staff to go hunting through file storage for that all important document. Smart Records Group offers a full range of records management services including storage. Melbourne based, our secure facility in Moorabbin offers excellent protection for your important records and we also offer same day delivery services. We are also able to offer a range of digital solutions from bureau scanning through to high end EDMS systems.
